Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.93,0:02:06.64,Kar,,0,0,0,,{\k33}ya{\k18}ga{\k24}te {\k48}ji{\k24}yu{\k43}u {\k23}ni {\k27}to{\k20}bi{\k26}ma{\k19}wa{\k20}re{\k46}ru
