Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.77,0:02:09.48,Kar,,0,0,0,,{\k28}ha{\k35}ne {\k34}wo {\k23}te{\k43}ni {\k24}i{\k23}re{\k62}te
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.77,0:02:09.48,EndOPED,,0,0,0,,with which I could fly freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.27,0:02:14.32,Kar,,0,0,0,,{\k22}mu{\k31}ku {\k36}na {\k30}hi{\k42}to{\k31}mi {\k39}wa {\k35}mo{\k35}to{\k34}me{\k34}te{\k34}ku
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.27,0:02:14.32,EndOPED,,0,0,0,,I want to go to the end of the skies
