Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.40,0:02:18.03,Kar,,0,0,0,,{\k28}so{\k19}ra {\k18}no {\k51}mu{\k24}ko{\k23}u {\k21}he {\k16}i{\k31}ki{\k22}ta{\k43}i {\k66}na
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.40,0:02:18.03,EndOPED,,0,0,0,,which my pure eyes desire.
