Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.49,0:02:28.08,EndOPED,,0,0,0,,I feel that it should be to grab onto a dream
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.56,0:02:33.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰にも譲りたくはない\N夢を掴みたいと思うよ
